                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/8690" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">MIS-0267</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2411 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">以“钉”促“敏”：林清轩如何通过业务数字化塑造组织敏捷性？</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Promoting “agility” through “Ding”: How can Lin Qingxuan build organizational agility through business digitization?</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">孙元，杨平泊，闻肖融，傅金娣</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">浙江工商大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">上海林清轩生物科技有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">轻工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">业务数字化；组织敏捷性；价值共创；2024百优案例；微案例；重点项目；系列4-1</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Business digitization; Organizational agility; Value Co-Creation</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">随着数字技术的飞速发展，兼营制造与零售的传统企业正迎来业务数字化转型的必然趋势。这一转型不仅关乎企业持续发展的战略，还极大地推动企业能够形成快速适应市场变化和高效资源配置的敏捷性。本案例详述了中国化妆品品牌林清轩从2016年始，果断摒弃陈旧的线下经营观念，全方位推进业务数字化转型，并同步构建敏捷化组织体系的发展历程。尽管林清轩在转型之途中不得不直面线上线下零售融合冲突、传统组织模式局限以及产品创新步伐滞缓等诸多难题。但在品牌创始人孙来春的带领下，林清轩通过深入运用钉钉等数字化工具，成功实施了新零售战略、构建了线上组织体系，并对组织架构进行了精细化调整，这一系列举措在林清轩的销售业绩提升、内部管理优化、产品创新提速等多个维度上产生了显著效果，最终完成了组织整体升级和敏捷化改造。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">With the rapid development of digital technology, traditional enterprises that also engage in manufacturing and retail are facing an inevitable trend of business digital transformation. This transformation not only concerns the sustainable development strategy of the enterprise, but also greatly promotes the agility of the enterprise to quickly adapt to market changes and efficiently allocate resources. This case describes the development process of Chinese cosmetics brand Lin Qingxuan, which has decisively abandoned outdated offline business concepts since 2016, comprehensively promoted business digital transformation, and synchronously built an agile organizational system. Although Lin Qingxuan had to face many challenges during his transformation, such as conflicts between online and offline retail integration, limitations of traditional organizational models, and slow pace of product innovation. But under the leadership of brand founder Sun Laichun, Lin Qingxuan successfully implemented a new retail strategy, built an online organizational system, and made fine adjustments to the organizational structure through in-depth use of digital tools such as DingTalk. This series of measures had significant effects on Lin Qingxuan&#39;s sales performance improvement, internal management optimization, product innovation acceleration, and other dimensions, ultimately completing the overall upgrade and agile transformation of the organization.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《企业战略管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">业务数字化过程；组织敏捷性；价值共创理论</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024-10</td>
                            </tr>
